# INGEST — send your answer to the system (required)

**Ingest is how your Cursor reply enters SourceA / SinaPromptOS execution truth.** It is **not** “wait for the next order.” It is **reporting** completed work.

After every VERIFY:

1. End the chat reply with the fenced YAML below (all required fields, real `reported_at` UTC).
2. Write the **full reply** (prose + YAML) to `reports/cursor-reply-latest.txt`.

ASF (or automation) ingests on Mac — **do not modify** SinaPromptOS scripts:

```bash
~/Desktop/SinaPromptOS/scripts/ingest-cursor-reply.sh noetfield reports/cursor-reply-latest.txt
```

**Planning** still comes from Noetfield `os/plan.json` — not from waiting on dispatch.

```yaml
schema_version: 1
repo: noetfield
task: "<os/plan.json task you completed>"
status: done | blocked | partial
verify_passed: true | false
verify_command: "<command you ran>"
verify_output_summary: "<one line result>"
blocked_reason: ""
next_action: ""
evidence_paths: []
reported_at: "2026-06-04T12:00:00Z"
reporter: cursor
```

Missing `reported_at` breaks ingest — include it every time.
